Subject:    <a href="?t=95837889500032&r=1&w=2">Re: MR, MG, and MB records</a>
From:       <a href="?a=95837785000010&r=1&w=2">brian () sdcsvax ! ucsd ! edu  (Brian Kantor)</a>
